In the Matter of Windsor Park Nursing Home, Appellant, v Charles J. Hynes, as Deputy Attorney-General of the State of New York, Respondent. Submitted April 18, 1977; decided April 28, 1977

Reported below, 56 AD2d 872.

Motion for stay of enforcement of subpoena issued October 15, 1976 and of Appellate Division order entered March 14, 1977 granted.
